quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Competition has distracted you
  102,2,until you visit graveyards
  102,3,Nevertheless you soon will know
  102,4,"once more, you soon shall know"
  102,5,"Of course, if you realized with absolute certainty"
  102,6,how you will (all) see Hades
  102,7,"then you would see it with the [very] eye of certainty"
  102,8,next you will be questioned concerning bliss on that day